        "body": "Preview: https://clawhub-ui-design-refactor-fbyz6vrid.vercel.app\n\n## Summary\n\n- Refreshes the homepage hero, listing, popular creators, app shortcuts, BYOS/CLI section, and global footer styling.\n- Adds homepage skill/plugin listing controls with Top/Trending/New and Official/Top/New tabs, category filtering, search, pagination, and mobile layout polish.\n- Standardizes the footer across pages and removes the secondary footer variant.\n- Optimizes the footer/BYOS artwork path with smaller WebP assets.\n\n## Tests\n\n- `bun run test -- src/__tests__/home-route.test.tsx src/__tests__/ui-design-contract.test.ts src/__tests__/home-listing-section.test.tsx src/__tests__/packages-route.test.tsx`\n- `bun run test -- src/components/Footer.test.tsx`\n- `bun run ci:static`\n- `bun run ci:unit`\n- `bun run build`\n- `vercel deploy --yes --force`\n- `curl -I -L https://clawhub-ui-design-refactor-fbyz6vrid.vercel.app/` → `HTTP/2 200`\n\n## Review\n\n- `codex --config service_tier=fast review --base upstream/main` found category/search pagination issues; fixed in this branch.\n- Final rerun was attempted, but the Codex CLI hit usage quota before completing.\n",
